lass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d08c8c77cfbf57a48a44003de7d3c7e9276111","tid":1336190,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:11:22.000Z","msg":"濃茶<br />\n唔好飲redbull嗰d 一散就仲累過唔飲"},{"pid":"b873647471b629d7b4418a677c424b24d9dd7cd7","tid":1336190,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"35965dbfb3abae6e44367a931a9ad0e553fee65e","tid":1336190,"uid":247082,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:03:08.000Z","msg":"提提大家，提神飲品一日唔可飲超過兩大罐，亦唔可以再飲酒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係曾經死過人架。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，飲完可能精神啲，但唔代表有活力。而精神時效因人而異，過咗鐘係要還架，之後會攰返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你估叫雞唔洗畀錢啊。<br />\n<br />\n建議各位都係有定時嘅生理時鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，瞓覺要無光環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，瞓前無撳電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:12:55.000Z","msg":"睡眠質素都好重要 如果樓主話訓到7個鐘都keep住眼訓 應該有呢方面問題"},{"pid":"43aa8f8d58883925963cc04e53a0996702aa6640","tid":1336190,"uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9d08c8c77cfbf57a48a44003de7d3c7e9276111","tid":1336190,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:11:22.000Z","msg":"濃茶<br />\n唔好飲redbull嗰d 一散就仲累過唔飲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T21:57:52.000Z","msg":"剛剛買左兩支redbull......"},{"pid":"c042381e71e214b3af030d3f9bb5538af46d5681","tid":1336190,"uid":118351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43aa8f8d58883925963cc04e53a0996702aa6640","tid":1336190,"uid":30067,"like